APPLE COMPUTER, INC.

PLAINTIFFS FILED THIS PURPORTED CLASS ACTION IN SAN

FRANCISCO COUNTY SUPERIOR COURT ON FEBRUARY 17, 2005. THE COMPLAINT

ALLEGES VIOLATIONS OF CALIFORNIA BUSINESS & PROFESSIONS CODE

§17200 (UNFAIR COMPETITION) AND

VIOLATION OF THE CONSUMER LEGAL REMEDIES ACT (CLRA) REGARDING A VARIETY OF

