RESEARCH LTD. V. APPLE COMPUTER, INC., ET AL.

PLAINTIFF GOBELI

RESEARCH LTD. FILED THIS PATENT INFRINGEMENT ACTION AGAINST THE COMPANY

AND SUN MICROSYSTEMS, INC. ON APRIL 15, 2004 IN THE UNITED STATES

DISTRICT COURT FOR THE EASTERN DISTRICT OF TEXAS, MARSHALL DIVISION, ALLEGING

INFRINGEMENT OF U.S. PATENT 5,418,968 RELATED TO A SYSTEM AND METHOD OF

