POTENTIALLY DILUTIVE

SECURITIES REPRESENTING APPROXIMATELY 12.4 MILLION, 8.7 MILLION, AND 101.6 MILLION

SHARES OF COMMON STOCK FOR THE YEARS ENDED SEPTEMBER 24, 2005,

